item.title: Quasisymmetric minimality on packing dimension for homogeneous perfect sets
item.description: arXiv:2407.20562v1 Announce Type: new Abstract: In this paper, we study the quasisymmetric packing minimality of homogeneous perfect sets, and obtain that a special class of homogeneous perfect sets with $\operatorname{dim}_{P}E=1$ is quasisymmetrically packing minimal.
item.dc:creator: Shishuang Liu, Yanzhe Li, Jiaojiao Yang

item.title: The weak Extension Principle
item.description: arXiv:2407.20791v1 Announce Type: cross Abstract: We prove a rigidity result for maps between \v{C}ech-Stone remainders under fairly mild forcing axioms.
item.dc:creator: Alessandro Vignati, Deniz Yilmaz
